messages.message: [Webservice consolidation] Hi all, I am working on consolidating webservices (api-server, api-server-apps, apps-server, webapp etc). The second PR in this series is here (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/30648). I plan to merge this over the weekend/Monday morning IST. Please DM me if you are working on these parts of our codebase and want me to wait. I did a similar exercise a while back.(https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1662970464098349)
